      "content": "idk i'm kinda hesitant to go to a clinic right now tbh, im super busy with finals and it's like an hour away. plus i feel okay now, just a bit slow. u sure a salt/lemon water thing will fix it? seems a bit simple for how much it actually hurt for a sec. would it be safe to just take some ibuprofen and sleep it off for a few hours instead?",
